# ─── Heavy binary artifacts in the v0.1.0/ tree ───
# Only checksums and small metadata are tracked; the actual installers
# come from the workflow's release job (upload-artifact + gh-release).
*.deb
*.rpm
*.AppImage
*.exe
*.msi
*.dmg
*.apk
*.aab
*.ipa
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.tar.bz2
*.tar.xz
*.zip
*.7z
*.bin
# But KEEP the *.sha256 / *CHECKSUM* / *SHA256* / *RELEASE_NOTES* / *.txt files
!*.sha256
!*.sha1
!*CHECKSUM*
!*SHA256*
!*RELEASE_NOTES*
!*.txt
!*.md

